Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.64,0:00:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.59,0:00:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.02,0:00:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,別…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.28,0:00:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.23,0:00:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那女孩 羽鳥智世
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.61,0:02:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在日本已被登記死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.49,0:02:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就在這邊隨便選個地區把她加進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,有勞了 阿道夫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不 多虧您告訴了我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,夜之寵兒很貴重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(820,982)}Slay Vega
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,有天資或意願的孩子都是財產啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這是當…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.11,0:02:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你很喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不喜歡和你一起喝！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.46,0:02:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這是愛麗絲送的聖誕禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.68,0:02:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,就一杯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,現在有空嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.02,0:02:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,托里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊 兩個人都板著臉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,要進來就給我安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,在喝酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,也算我一個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,別隨便碰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你這手還沒修好？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是叫卡塔菲爾斯…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,之後還有過接觸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊 也給我介紹一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,跨世紀的漂流魔術師是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不老不死是永遠的主題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,無聊的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你潔癖還真嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然你很優秀 但這點很得罪人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,夥伴在精不在多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,托里 不能再倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛啊 就一點沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我並不優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,要是優秀就不會被那種傢伙威脅了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.83,0:03:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 超好玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這沒四個小時完不了的 你慢慢享受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這啥啊 超麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你也來喝！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.20,0:04:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}阿道夫救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.50,0:04:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,別拽我！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 搞啥啊 不是只有阿道夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,梅麗托莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,妖精？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我以前老師的使魔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,倫敦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:04:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.89,0:05:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,身體感覺很輕盈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,喉嚨也不癢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,冷暖也很適宜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.97,0:05:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,請問 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.73,0:05:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,卡塔菲爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.86,0:05:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,咦…我的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.17,0:05:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是叫卡塔菲爾斯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐你是透明的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,難道是幽靈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊 你得去你該去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,因為 不這樣就很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 對不起 對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,卡塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我不叫這個受盡詛咒的名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,卡塔菲爾斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,約瑟夫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.09,0:06:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,卡塔菲爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要怎樣才能得到救贖？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:06:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你去了誰那兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是他…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,卡塔菲爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他的聲音不絕於耳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,今天第幾天了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你只睡了兩天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這…為啥林德爾先生的海豹人會在這啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(1163.667,982)}selchidh
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你總算醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.19,0:07:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你醒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.34,0:07:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我去告訴大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,該說有點麻煩吧…出了點不太好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,隨便給你挑件衣服穿可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,謝…謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,話說 愛麗絲你幾歲？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,今年18了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:07:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那很好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,早 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.58,0:08:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.70,0:08:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,艾利亞斯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.47,0:08:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.34,0:08:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我第一次能這麼好好觀察活的夜之寵兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.34,0:08:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(1390.667,982)}Slay Vega
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,很高興見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你能活著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不太想說他是我同事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,0:08:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我同事真是失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,幸會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.30,0:08:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫阿道夫·施特勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.84,0:08:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,幸會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那時很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.82,0:08:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,請不要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫托里·依尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以叫我托里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.09,0:09:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是學院的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,學院？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒聽說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,閒聊就免了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,能趕緊進入正題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我們已經跟他說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.63,0:09:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,在龍之國的幼龍被密獵了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,被綁走的有兩頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,密獵者留下了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我做的移動裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這次的事恐怕是卡塔菲爾斯做的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.22,0:09:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,連同手臂一起這裝置的技巧也被偷取了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這事兒無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我也明白這不是你的本意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.01,0:09:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,問題是為何我們也得一起去找卡塔菲爾斯和龍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:10:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你們和龍之國有交情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,也熟悉卡塔菲爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,說來為何學院會尋找龍？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,林德爾大人和學院締結過協議
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,和林德爾先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.02,0:10:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你能幫忙找回龍並將之還回林德爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.56,0:10:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你朋友那邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這也是幫被束縛在那邊的他的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.53,0:10:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,艾利亞斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.85,0:10:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,和我們沒關係 還很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你忘了自己身體有多脆弱了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.17,0:10:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,艾利亞斯才是別忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.32,0:10:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這很疼 很痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.28,0:10:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.86,0:11:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你說得對 我們沒義務也沒責任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但幼龍們並不是像我這樣自願離鄉背井的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,坐視和我一起玩的孩子們留下痛苦回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.59,0:11:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,謝…謝謝你！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.01,0:11:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他有點變了…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,於是 你們有眉目和線索嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,關於卡塔菲爾斯是完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,林德爾倒是有向我們提供龍的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.42,0:11:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但那兩頭龍意識微弱 他也很難確定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我想卡塔菲爾斯可能在倫敦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:11:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,為何這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.37,0:12:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,大概…是直覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,施特勞德先生 龍能賣出高價嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,當然能啊 很高的價哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那說不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 誰能借我用下電話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你好？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.97,0:12:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.42,0:12:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那就行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在在巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.99,0:12:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是工作 我會根據金額和內容決定是否接受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊再用點力壓住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,塞斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不見了啊 智世小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.69,0:13:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…這是恩滋華斯先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.69,0:13:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法魔術之類應當不能在競拍場內使用才是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,就是聽說過了 才沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是整個重構了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不是賽門先生也不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.39,0:13:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那張臉是誰的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不問各位的名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…可以的話希望有所幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:13:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:13:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這個就放在下午第一個做暖場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,之後再開始正式的競拍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你可滿意？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.35,0:14:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,龍的競拍在下午六點開始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,在此之前幾位請隨意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你這邊賣東西真是隨心所欲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,智世小姐 這個請收下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,支票簿和卡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.73,0:14:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你當初拍出的金額已有半數入帳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,半…半數？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,這是身為商品同時也是商品提供方的你應得的份
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,龍的價格很高昂的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.10,0:14:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,學院一方經費若有不足時盡可使用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.69,0:14:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,錢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.55,0:14:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,說來這本是艾利亞斯的錢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺變了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你長高了 和那時真是判若兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有變的地方也有一如既往的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.95,0:15:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,關鍵的部分幾乎未變
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.19,0:15:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好壞不論 你真是頑固得很啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.31,0:15:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,怎了 在說啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,話說 你不來學院嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在家有人會覺得寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,確實是軟硬不吃 厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼話 但說無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.47,0:15:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒跟她提過學院的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她不會去學院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,所以沒必要說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你如何處理信使的 破壞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.74,0:15:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這不像你啊 連富烈德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼執著於夜之寵兒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.13,0:15:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(1124,982)}Slay Vega
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我並非在意夜之寵兒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(1124,982)}Slay Vega
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,而是在意身為人類的她的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就算她眼下無礙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.71,0:15:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但將來她所能依靠的若只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,今後她的成長又將如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我們該討論的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,讓沒有目標的人 背負知識的金庫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.18,0:16:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,將其趕上駛向前方的航船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,佯裝對其指點前路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,令其深信再無別途
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你我並無二致 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.29,0:16:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,難道你…其實並不想成為魔術師？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是被人強迫的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,別隨便決定我的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,智世就是這麼期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,能持續到何時 容我拭目以待
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,生物是會變的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.45,0:16:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不論期望與否
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,感…感覺好尷尬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,但那塊骨頭沒想明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.27,0:17:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,即便最初行進在指定好的路線上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但最終走上只屬於自己道路的人數不勝數
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.38,0:17:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你在走自己的路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.04,0:17:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,自己做出選擇後所走的才是自己的路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.07,0:17:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,年輕真好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來我們開始六點的競拍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.02,0:17:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,如今與世隔絕的北方的龍之國
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,生長在那裡的純種翼龍種的幼龍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那從80萬起拍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.84,0:18:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,81
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,82
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.59,0:18:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,85
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,90
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,90！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,92
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.45,0:18:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,100
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,150以下學院都勉強能支付
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,要是超過了就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,出貨的人是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.91,0:18:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,122
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,代理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,還是代理的代理？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,125
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,125
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那個人在看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,150
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.13,0:18:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,150
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.39,0:18:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,要出到什麼價位？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就你所知我帳戶上的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.05,0:18:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,160
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,170
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.91,0:18:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,還有出價的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:18:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,還有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.61,0:19:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.49,0:19:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你才能聽見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,對你來說很方便的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,方便…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,180
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.09,0:19:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,180
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.92,0:19:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,185
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,185
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.94,0:19:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,191
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,191
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,193
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,193
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.78,0:19:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,197
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我們這邊資金見底了就拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,否則就作罷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,耳邊的約定可真是遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,請各位不要留下遺憾 意下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,260
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:19:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,290
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,290
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,看來能行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,2 290！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,現價290
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.18,0:20:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,還有哪位出價高過290？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是專用的強化束縛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,為何被打破了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,從來沒這樣過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.57,0:21:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼看都…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.60,0:21:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,…瘋了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.67,0:21:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,智世？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,它想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.42,0:21:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,它很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,它很討厭現在的環境
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.80,0:21:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你能聽到龍的聲音嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.24,0:22:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.64,0:22:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那些不是你的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.14,0:22:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,無需為其所束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.73,0:22:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不好！
